sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Note over browser: User types note in SPA and clicks Save
    browser->>server: POST /new_note_spa (JSON data: content + date)
    activate server
    server-->>browser: 201 Created
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: SPA updates UI locally (no reload)
    Note right of browser: redrawNotes() renders new note immediately
    Note right of browser: No additional HTTP requests needed